{"tid":883940,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"又再一單行飛鵝山報警要人救","createTime":"2018-10-31T08:18:37.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-31T08:42:30.000Z","uid":19287,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"f21089d4abc1876d25e2b0bf2991d2954c66d024","tid":883940,"uid":19287,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-31T08:18:37.000Z","msg":"【15:00】警員見到事主在山上，雙方有一段距離，正前往接觸<br />\n<br />\n正當救援人員在飛鵝山搜索懷疑迷路的行山女子同時﹝ <a href=\"http://bit.ly/2Jrrdb3\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2Jrrdb3&d=VbFC7LBVfuEwia6Eu%2FVbe8VakpCEQgWe3bOYm8oES40%3D&h=9c71142b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2Jrrdb3</a> ﹞，警方再接獲市民報案，在飛鵝山自殺崖迷路。上午11時左右，一名男子報警，表示行自殺崖路中迷路。警方、消防員、救護員到場搜索。<br />\n<br />\n自殺崖位於飛鵝山西南的山脊頂上，巨大而直垂的崖壁陡峻危險，惟沿途能盡覽東九龍一帶景色，近年被捧為行山熱點，亦是拍照及打卡勝地。有行山專家指沿自殺崖上飛鵝山路段地勢險要，且多碎石，沒有配備攀石裝備的行山人士，絕不適宜冒險攀登。去年11月29日，48歲康文署女職員，偕友人行山，在自殺崖失足墮20米喪命 。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/31/161825_9d4be0e149519b0b8b54cf5aafe79e55.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F31%2F161825_9d4be0e149519b0b8b54cf5aafe79e55.png&h=dbd62f82&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/31/161827_45f7724bff50ece262d2742b2ac8c688.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F31%2F161827_45f7724bff50ece262d2742b2ac8c688.png&h=83fa34ae&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d6355034c76e5629b68f1fd4d68592d75088bb1e","tid":883940,"uid":25643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-31T08:41:09.000Z","msg":"其實條路線唔難﹐不過個名得人驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74d84e78494532482de4194801de07cecc813d27","tid":883940,"uid":102096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-31T08:42:30.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}